FBIS3-17765 "drsov060_a_94017" FBIS-SOV-94-060 Document Type:Daily Report 29 Mar 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Foreign Ministry Keeping Close Watch LD2903101094 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 0756 GMT 29 Mar 94 LD2903101094 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [By ITAR-TASS diplomatic correspondent] [Text] Moscow, 29 Mar -- The Russian Federation Ministry of Foreign Affairs is keeping a close watch on the deteriorating situation in Algeria. A senior spokesman for the Russian Foreign Ministry told an ITAR-TASS correspondent that the Foreign Ministry is in constant contact with the Algerian side. He pointed out that the circumstances of the terrorist act against the Russian citizen are being investigated, and that exhaustive information from the Algerian side is expected on the affair.
